{"tid":1505594,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"致香港黑狗的信[I want to play a game]","createTime":"2019-08-25T14:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T00:22:59.000Z","uid":207374,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb1656975ba16e0e547bbfc0c5af4371ad4a8ab","tid":1505594,"uid":207374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 轉載信息&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致：香港所有黑色的狗隻<br />\n<br />\n     2我們不會害怕你們鎮壓人民的手段，我們香港人永遠不會忘記你們對香港市民的所作行為！0你們不懂得珍惜人的生命，不知道人的生命是無價！你們只是被權力控制的一群傀儡！1很抱歉，你們踏上了不能讓香港市民原諒的道路。在這裏給你們所有黑狗99一個忠告！在你們現正還生活的時間內，請你們好好珍惜！因為你們前面有一個重大的生命考驗。1想讓你們知道，其實人的生命是多麼的渺小，是多麼的難能可貴。因此，你們要時刻保持警覺，只要你們還是香港的黑狗，我們<span style=\"color: red;\">就會行動</span>！<br />\n<br />\n                                                                                香港人字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊戲.....開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bvnhtv5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbvnhtv5.png&h=c5c35ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18revKr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18revKr.png&h=e397fcbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21b23c23772224759165f4709230017d340a29dd","tid":1505594,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:51:07.000Z","msg":"【置頂】828 metoo集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"44d6a92483cef645122d3d3fb31ebf4931504b05","tid":1505594,"uid":148824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:52:27.000Z","msg":"內容幾好 係睇得辛苦少少<br />\n<br />\n對敵人仁慈=對自己殘忍<br />\n<a href=\"ht